lz</b> not firing a single shot during his pheasant hunt photo-op. My colle=
ague <b>John</b> <b>Heilemann</b> distilled the anxiety-inducing dynamics i=
n his newsletter yesterday, which you can read <u><a href=3D"https://email.=
